description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=2/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=1/3. A radioactive stick figure hedgehog has defeated Skyfish and destroyed the world. An angry Skyfish must fight, mine, and blast through time against flying zombies, an insane ex-girlfriend, a floating head, and his greatest nemesis and save the world from awful parody again, again.
